	(text_box "HARDWARE DESIGN CONSIDERATIONS:\n- Border/space around the clock IC\n- Clock trace isolation\n- Impedance matching (USB, SPI, RF)\n- Length matching\n- Solid GND plane under high speed signals and RF\n- Decoupling capacitors\n- Power outtput filtering (remove harmonics)\n- Stitching vias beside signal vias\n"
